    features_test.csv
    grid.json
    preprocess_stats.json
  ucsd_ped1/
    features_train.csv
    features_test.csv
    grid.json
    preprocess_stats.json
  avenue/
    features_train.csv
    features_test.csv
    grid.json
    preprocess_stats.json
```

Kích thước hiện tại theo `preprocess_stats.json`:

```text
